docs/qa/BUG_BACKLOG.md:8:| DS-P1-002 | High | Partner booking fulfillment | Normalize partner booking mutations around the authenticated principal. Remove request-body/query `partner_session_token` rebinding from booking action, document, arrangement, complaint, close, and report endpoints so booking ownership comes from the auth helper only. | open | Add partner-booking regressions proving a foreign token cannot mutate another partner's booking, documents, complaints, or close/report routes. Source: `booking/manage_partner_booking.py:394-643`; `booking/manage_partner_booking.py:646-940`; `booking/manage_partner_booking.py:1378-1774` |
